<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Major+Mono+Display|Montserrat|Saira+Stencil+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='./stylesheets/style.css'/>


    <title><%= title %></title>

  </head>

  <body>
  	<div><%- partial('partials/navbar') -%></div>


    <div class="jumbotron col-md container-fluid jumbotron-fluid">
        <h1 class="animated fadeInDown"></h1>
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to EasyRider</h1>
        <br><br><br>
        <h4 >The Artist Hospitality Helper</h4>
    </div>

     <div class="row">
      <div class="container col-md-6" id="card1">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Behind the Scenes</h5>
            <p class="card-text">The festival industry has been around for about 60 years, and as a young industry, we haven’t caught up to technology, and it’s about time we do.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container col-md-6" id="card2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">The Challenge</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Festival numbers are at an all time high, both in the number of existing festivals as well as in the number of people attending. As festivals grow, the process of making them happen gets harder when we don't have the proper technology backing us up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

        <div class="container col-md-12" id="card3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Why Use EasyRider</h5>
            <p class="card-text">EasyRider creates a solution to all these problems by providing a software and paired smart phone application. 
            It sorts all the items asked for in the many riders received and creates a compiled list.
            This list can be filtered by item type, who it’s for, and what stage it goes to, allowing for a one-stop-shop for the artist hospitality team to use.
            <br>
            This makes it easier to shop, distribute, and keep the artists happy!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <div><%- partial('partials/footer') -%></div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>


